title: The Samsung Galaxy Tab Book Volume 1 - 2014  UK
description:
The Samsung Galaxy Tab Book Volume 1 - 2014  UK

180 Pages | True PDF | English | 27 MB 


The Samsung Galaxy Tab Book is the ideal companion for your device. Discover top tips for making the most of your Galaxy Tab at work, home and on the go, before delving into in-depth masterclasses on its in-built apps. Follow the step-by-step tutorials and set up your device so it works best for you. Make the most of features you never even knew existed, and you'll become a pro in no time at all. Featuring: Your life & Samsung - Discover how to get the most of your Galaxy Tab at home, work and on the go. Settings - Tweak the settings to make your tablet work best for you. Samsung Apps - Search for and download apps, then learn to manage them. Google Drive - Manage all of your documents and get others involved.
